#{{idiom}} to [[steal]], [[cheat]] or [[swindle]]
#to [[copy]], especially [[illegal]]ly
#to [[charge]] an [[exorbitant]] or [[unfair]] rate

====Translations====
*French: [[arracher]] (1)
*Spanish: [[arrancar]] (1),[[estafar]] (2 or 4)

===Noun===
'''[[rip]] [[off]]''', '''[[rip-off]]'''
# a bad or [[deal]]; an unfair [[price]] or [[rate]]
# a [[theft]] or [[robbery]]
# a [[scam]]
# a [[copy]], especially one that is illegal or [[inferior]]

